item.title: About
item.description: Hello there!, I’m Ojas Singh, and this is my personal webpage. My interests lie at the intersection of chemistry, quantum computing, and machine learning. I like solving problems and have wide range of interests generally revolving around writing computer code to make sense of complex things. I love writing codes in Rust. Currently, I am in the final semester of my BS-MS (chemistry) dual degree program at the Indian Institute of Science Education and Research Mohali, India.
